# Handoff — Pack #6 (observability-baseline) Phase 0.5a complete

## What was done

**Phase 0.5a (the `afa-storage` crate) of Pack #6
(`observability-baseline`)** is complete and green. The
shared SQLite-backed storage wrapper exists with the three
locked methods (`open`, `migrate`, `with_conn`) and the
re-exported `StorageError` enum from `afa-contracts`. No
engine has been refactored onto it yet (that's Phase 0.5b).

